                                                 <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-indigo-600/60 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 flex items-center justify-center text-white transition-opacity"><Download size={20}/></div>
                                              </a>))}
                                         </div>
                                       )}
                                    </div>
                                  );
                                })}
                              </div>
                           </div>
                         );
